package.name: asymptix/php-html-dom-parser
package.description: Composer adaptation and wrapper for the Simple HTML DOM parser written on PHP5+ let you manipulate HTML in a very easy and fast way. It supports invalid HTML DOM and may find tags in HTML DOM with selectors just like jQuery.
